<!-- About Section (Optional) -->
<section id="about" class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-12 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
                <h3>About<span> Us</span></h3>
                <p class="mb-1">The birth of the Coffeeshop Company can be traced back to 1999 when the first Coffeeshop opened its doors to its guests on a historical September day in Vienna.</p>
                <p>Characterized by a very special and unimitable atmosphere, the Coffeeshop Company is a new, unique interpretation of the ever-popular traditional Viennese coffee house culture, which was included in the UNESCO list of "intangible cultural heritage" in 2011.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-12">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/800x400?text=About+Us" class="img-fluid about-img" alt="About Image">
